    <h1>Place ID</h1>
    <p class="description">A unique textual identifier Google assigns to every location in Google Maps — businesses, landmarks, transit stops — creating a <strong>stable, permanent reference</strong> used across all Google services and the Places API.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
